<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFBBFFC5C5EC01E597B8F853" author="Tikader, B. K." box="[500,659,1943,1969]" pageId="12" pageNumber="401" pagination="274 - 277" refId="ref8564" refString="Tikader, B. K. (1977) Description of two new species of jumping-spider of the genus Rhene (family: Salticidae) from India. Proceedings of the Indian Academy of Science, 85 (B), 274 - 277. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / BF 03052378" type="journal article" year="1977">Tikader, 1977</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was originally described from 
<collectingRegion id="0551F878FFBBFFC5C01801E591A7F853" box="[1024,1164,1943,1969]" country="India" name="Maharashtra" pageId="12" pageNumber="401">Maharashtra</collectingRegion>
