<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFBBFFC5C5DC01AD97F9F81B" author="Biswas, B. &amp; Biswas, K." box="[452,722,2015,2041]" pageId="12" pageNumber="401" pagination="357 - 500" refId="ref6755" refString="Biswas, B. &amp; Biswas, K. (1992) Araneae: Spiders. State Fauna Series 3: Fauna of West Bengal, 3, 357 - 500." type="journal article" year="1992">Biswas &amp; Biswas, 1992</bibRefCitation>
). Based on the detailed examination of the 
<typeStatus id="182E8838FFBBFFC5C0B601AD91C2F81B" box="[1198,1257,2015,2041]" pageId="12" pageNumber="401">types</typeStatus>
